resources.string: "Tsohon iri kaza ba zai dauki sabon iri kaza ba"
"Kana so ka fice daga dawo da kwafe da gaske?"
"In ka danna maballin gogewa, zai goge duk fayalolin kwafe karkashin Cibiyar masarrafai. Ka tabbatar ko kana son ka goge?"
"Ka zabi bayanan da kake so ka dawo da"
"babu wani masarrafi da za a dawo da"
"katin ma\'adana na waje ba za a iya isa gare shi ba, ba za ka iya shiga masarrafin kwafe ba"
"Ka zabi APP daya ko bayanai akalla"
"Ma\'adanar waje ba ta, ka duba ma\'adanar waje na na\'urar"
"In ka danna maballin gogewa,zai goge apk. Ka tabbatar ko kana so a goge?"
"Wurin ma\'adanar ya yi kadan, ka goge katin SD na bayanai"
"Wurin ma\'adanar ya yi kadan, ka goge Ma\'adanar bayanai na ciki"
"Kuma bayanan ba za a dawo da su ba bayan gogewa. Ka tabbatar kana so ka goge bayanan?"
"An kammala dawo da bayanai. Za a iya samun kwafe na bayanan.Shin a goge kwafen bayanan?"
"Wadannan bayanan ba su dace da gogewa ba!"
Sararin ma\'adanar ciki ya yi kadan, yi amfani da ma\'adanar waje
"karanta a matsayin bayanan mai amfani da"

resources.string: ""Yi madadi kuma mayar" siffofi ne da aka yi su don siffofin wayar mobayil na China, akwai shi a duk nau\'in wayar mobayil na China da aka daidaita su don amfani da juna."
"Wayar Mobayil ba katin SD, in kana son maido da data a sabuwar wayar mobayil, ta katin SD ko a kwamfuta za a yi tiransifa nasa ga maido da sabon madadin fayil na wayar mobayil."

"Sauyawa da katin SD:1, Katin SD a cikin na\'urar; 2, yi madadi; 3, cire katin SD, soka sabuwar na\'urar; 4, bude a madadin sabuwar na\'urar da maido da masarrafin, zabi neman madadin fayil don maido da aikin maidowar. Ta hanyar sauya kamfutar: 1, madadi, duba hanyar yin madadin; 2, na\'urar an hada ta da kwamfuta kuma bude cibiyar adiresoshin wayar; 3, hanyar madadin ya yi kwafin madadin fayil ga kwamfutar; 4, sabuwar wayar mobayil hade take da kwamfutar kuma bude cibiyar adiresoshin sabuwar wayar mobayil; 5, fayil din madadi zai kwafu ga sabuwar waya kowane cibiyar adiresoshi; 6, bude sabon madadin na\'urar kuma maido da masarrafin, zabi neman fayil na madadi don maidowa a aikin maidowar. "

"1, na\'urar za a hada ta da kwamfuta kuma a bude cibiyar adiresoshin wayar mobayil;2, madadin / hanyar madadin fayil da aka kwafa zuwa kwamfuta; 3, sabon wayar mobayil yana hade da kwamfuta kuma bude cibiyar adiresoshin sabuwar wayar mobayil; 4, fayalolin madadi za a kwafe su ga cibiyar adiresoshin sabuwar wayar mobayil; 5, bude madadin sabuwar wayar mobayil da maido da masarrafin, zabi neman madadin fayil don maido da tsarin maidowar. "
"Wannan na\'urar ba shi da maido da data na katin SD, kamar yadda ake bukata a sabuwar na\'ura, ta hanyar kwamfuta za a yi tiransifa zuwa madadin fayil na sabuwar na\'urar don maidowa."
"tantance duk zai dauki lokaci mai tsawo, ka saurara..."
"Miss yana bukatar izinin kira. Don haka ba zai iya aiki sosai ba. A duba saitin izini."
"Wannan manhaja ba ta da damar amfani da rumbum ajiya na waje, A zabi ma\'ajiya ta ciki."
